  <Docs>
    <summary>
            Provides a mechanism for activating properties on Blazor component instances.
            </summary>
    <remarks>
            This interface allows customization of how properties marked with <see cref="T:Microsoft.AspNetCore.Components.InjectAttribute" />
            are populated on component instances. The default implementation uses the <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" />
            to resolve services for injection.
            </remarks>
  </Docs>
